title: Is the SEC down? League depth a question at midway point
text: > Texas Is the SEC down? League depth a question at midway point FILE - In this Sept. 26, 2015, file photo, LSU running back Leonard Fournette (7) gets past Syracuse cornerback Wayne Morgan (2) for a touchdown in the first half of an NCAA college football game in Syracuse, N.Y. Fournette has rushed for 1,202 yards when nobody else in FBS has reached 1,000. He's also second nationally in scoring with 14 touchdowns _ two more than Vanderbilt and Missouri have scored, respectively. (AP Photo/Mike Groll, File)
